"Femto Uploader" is an extension which allows you to shorten your the URLs of any page you visit at the click of a button.  Click the extension and it will generate a shortened URL using the https://v2.femto.pw URL shortener.

You can manage, update and delete your extensions created with this extension from https://v2.femto.pw.
